ost of scenarios. The \\texttt{R} and \\texttt{Stan} code\nto implement the proposed method is publicly available from Github\n(\\url{https://github.com/gunhanb/TITEPK_code}).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Feb 2020 16:18:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-18"}
